- No, it's not 'Why  did you spell  that last word 'Theatre?'  It looks  kind of pretentious, man.' Although I must admit, that one got asked a lot, too. (If you really must know, it  was in place before I got there, and inertia is a powerful  thing. I didn't  dare change the  name of the Angst stat in Wraith, either.)
